B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20modified%20Cybertruck%20has%20undergone%20a%20grueling%20regime%20of%20government%20tests%20in%20Switzerland%20to%20be%20registered%20as%20road-legal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeholzer%20said%20the%20vehicle%20had%20passed%20most%20of%20the%20major%20hurdles%20to%20get%20approved%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bmatter%20of%20time%26quot%3B%20before%20Teslab's%20first%20Cybertruck%20was%20registered%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20Europe%20may%20have%20to%20wait%2C%20however%20%E2%80%94%20Switzerland%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20and%20Seeholzer%20admitted%20that%20getting%20approval%20in%20the%20EU%20would%20be%20a%20lengthy%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243c0937a-2dce-44b7-8b7c-b5232c93b951%5C%22%3EA%20'lifestyle'%20vehicle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Europe's%20cautious%20approach%20to%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20the%20demand%20seems%20to%20be%20there.%20Seeholzer%20said%20that%20Teslab%20had%20already%20sold%20three%20of%20its%20five%20Cybertrucks%20and%20had%20received%20around%20400%20preorders%20as%20of%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20weight%20regulations%20meant%20that%20the%20first%20few%20European%20Cybertruck%20owners%20would%20have%20to%20treat%20their%20trucks%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blifestyle%26quot%3B%20vehicle%20and%20avoid%20traditional%20truck%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Switzerland%2C%20the%20maximum%20weight%20for%20a%20car%20is%20three%20and%20a%20half%20thousand%20kilograms.%20The%20%5Bmodified%5D%20Cybertruck%20is%20a%20bit%20under%20it%2C%20which%20means%20you%20cannot%20load%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeighing%20in%20at%203.5%20tons%2C%20the%20pickup%20will%20be%20a%20tight%20squeeze%20on%20European%20roads%2C%20which%20are%20often%20far%20narrower%20than%20in%20the%20US.%20Its%20sharp%20edges%20and%200-60mph%20time%20of%202.6%20seconds%20have%20also%20led%20some%20experts%20to%20compare%20it%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-safety-guideless-missile-experts-say-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eguided%20missile%20on%20wheels%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBruno%20Dvorsk%C3%BD%20thinks%20otherwise.%20The%20cofounder%20of%20Cybertruck.cz%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20registered%20in%20Czechia%20last%20year%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20October%20he%20had%20imported%20another%20Cybertruck%20into%20the%20country%20and%20planned%20to%20register%20it%20before%20crashing%20it%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDvorsk%C3%BD%20said%20Cybertruck.cz%20had%20added%20silicone%20coverings%20to%20blunt%20the%20Cybertruck's%20sharp%20edges%2C%20swapped%20out%20its%20red%20lights%20for%20yellow%20ones%20that%20comply%20with%20local%20rules%2C%20and%20added%20reversing%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20no%20less%20dangerous%20than%20other%20large%20pickups%20already%20available%20in%20Europe%2C%20and%20said%20detractors%20were%20%26quot%3Bbicycle%20riders%26quot%3B%20who%20lived%20%26quot%3Bsmall%26quot%3B%20lives%20and%20were%20jealous%20of%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20okay%2C%20but%20don't%20hate%20on%20other%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dvorsk%C3%BD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20parked%20by%20a%20river%20in%20Prague.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694e649304eda4732f2e21c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20in%20Prague.%3Cp%3Ecybertruck.cz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europeafrica.army.mil%2FPortals%2F19%2Fdocuments%2FCustoms%2F2025%2520HNrelease%2520-%2520Cybertrucks.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Army%20Customs%20Agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20Germany%20had%20denied%20requests%20for%20service%20members%20to%20bring%20their%20Cybertrucks%20into%20the%20country%20because%20the%20vehicle%20%26quot%3Bdeviates%20significantly%26quot%3B%20from%20EU%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20the%20Cybertruck%20violated%20European%20rules%20banning%20vehicles%20from%20having%20sharp%20edges%20and%20requiring%20speed%20limiters%20on%20anything%20weighing%20over%203.5%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20Tesla%20would%20likely%20eventually%20build%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-smaller-tesla-cybertruck-highly-likely-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmaller%20version%20of%20the%20pickup%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20global%20markets%20like%20Europe%20and%20China.%20There's%20been%20no%20sign%20that%20Tesla%20has%20any%20plans%20to%20do%20this%2C%20and%20the%20brand's%20sales%20have%20cratered%20in%20Europe%20this%20year%20amid%20backlash%20against%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20anyone%20looks%20at%20the%20facts%20and%20the%20applicable%20rules%2C%20it's%20clear%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20illegal%20in%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Nix%2C%20a%20policy%20manager%20at%20European%20think-tank%20Transport%20%26amp%3B%20Environment%2C%20which%20was%20among%20the%20signatories%20of%20the%20letter%20protesting%20the%20Czech%20Cybertruck%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENix%20said%20that%20he%20expects%20further%20attempts%20to%20put%20Cybertrucks%20on%20European%20roads%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bdiscontinued%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Germany's%20decision%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20impossible%20for%20anyone%20who%20imported%20a%20Cybertruck%20into%20Europe%20to%20get%20the%20necessary%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f79dca5dbc4fd10dab37cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeeholzer%20said%20he%20hoped%20to%20change%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20Cybertruck%20in%20Europe.%3Cp%3ERaven%20Seeholzer%2FTeslab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWould-be%20European%20Cybertruck%20owners%20do%20have%20one%20unlikely%20ally%3A%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20After%20the%20US%20president%20imposed%20a%20barrage%20of%20tariffs%20on%20the%20EU%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20two%20superpowers%20unveiled%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpolicy.trade.ec.europa.eu%2Fnews%2Fjoint-statement-united-states-european-union-framework-agreement-reciprocal-fair-and-balanced-trade-2025-08-21_en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eframework%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20trade%20deal%20in%20August%20that%20included%20a%20commitment%20to%20standardize%20vehicle%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20a%20group%20of%20European%20cities%2C%20non-profits%2C%20and%20safety%20campaigners%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20European%20regulators%20urging%20them%20not%20to%20accept%20US%20standards%2C%20warning%20that%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20Cybertruck-style%20vehicles%20on%20European%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeholzer%20said%20he%20hoped%20Teslab's%20plan%20to%20make%20the%20Cybertruck%20road-legal%20in%20Europe%20would%20change%20the%20perception%20of%20Tesla's%20most%20controversial%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20previous%20efforts%20to%20get%20the%20Cybertruck%20into%20Europe%2C%20some%20of%20which%20have%20used%20unmodified%20imported%20vehicles%2C%20have%20done%20more%20harm%20than%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20tried%20to%20really%20do%20something%20to%20change%20the%20car.%20They%20just%20did%20maybe%20things%20on%20the%20edges%2C%20maybe%20changed%20a%20few%20things%20on%20the%20lights%2C%20but%20nobody%20went%20all%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-quest-to-bring-the-cybertruck-to-europe-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766748661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694e63bc64858d02d21768aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-quest-to-bring-the-cybertruck-to-europe-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Cybertruck%20has%20been%20on%20sale%20in%20the%20US%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20but%20Tesla%20has%20shown%20no%20signs%20of%20brining%20its%20most%20divisive%20EV%20across%20the%20Atlantic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-quest-to-bring-the-cybertruck-to-europe-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20advise%20Citi's%20ultra-wealthy%20clients%20on%20their%20art.%20I%20always%20take%20these%20precautions%20when%20entering%20their%20homes.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carla%20Caputa%2C%20Citigroup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691b558fe1a9cbb014de559f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECarla%20Caputo%20says%20she%20always%20follows%20a%20few%20key%20rules%20when%20in%20clients'%20homes.%3Cp%3ECitigroup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECarla%20Caputo%20helps%20coordinate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-advisor-citi-bank-wealthy-clients-market-value-2025-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eart%20purchases%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20collections%20for%20Citi's%20high-net-worth%20clients.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20always%20takes%20a%20few%20key%20precautions%20when%20entering%20clients'%20homes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECaputo%20also%20manages%20shipping%20logistics%2C%20from%20arranging%20freight%20flights%20to%20dealing%20with%20huge%20crates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Carla%20Caputo%2C%20the%20art%20collections%20manager%20and%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20Citi%20Wealth's%20Art%20Advisory%20group%2C%20which%20supports%20clients%20in%20the%20private%20bank.%20She%20worked%20at%20the%20Guggenheim%20Museum%20and%20the%20Museum%20of%20Modern%20Art%20before%20joining%20Citi%20in%202023.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20anything%2C%20I%20think%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20high-level%20project%20manager%20for%20Citi's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-jets-billionaire-status-symbol-luxury-time-food-perks-savings-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh-net-worth%20clients%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Sometimes%20I%20help%20them%20loan%20art%20to%20museums%2C%20sometimes%20I%20write%20condition%20reports%2C%20and%20sometimes%20I%20work%20on%20installations%20in%20their%20homes%20or%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20clients%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-art-advisor-buying-first-piece-galleries-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epurchase%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20gallery%20or%20auction%2C%20installing%20it%20is%20often%20a%20long%2C%20expensive%20process.%20Once%20the%20art%20is%20paid%20for%2C%20I%20contact%20registrars%20and%20shipping%20managers%20to%20coordinate%20getting%20it%20into%20the%20client's%20space.%20Does%20the%20piece%20already%20have%20a%20crate%3F%20Does%20it%20have%20a%20travel%20frame%3F%20Will%20it%20fit%20on%20a%20passenger%20flight%2C%20or%20does%20it%20need%20to%20fly%20on%20a%20freight%20plane%3F%20And%20if%20it%20does%20need%20a%20freight%20plane%2C%20how%20will%20it%20get%20to%20one%20of%20the%20few%20hubs%20that%20accommodate%20those%20flights%3F%20What%20route%20will%20it%20take%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20piece%2C%20deliver%20it%20to%20the%20client's%20home%20or%20office%2C%20retrieve%20it%2C%20and%20unpack%20it.%20Next%20comes%20figuring%20out%20storage%20%E2%80%94%20are%20we%20keeping%20the%20crate%20or%20throwing%20it%20away%3F%20If%20we're%20keeping%20it%2C%20where%20is%20it%20getting%20stored%3F%20To%20make%20it%20even%20more%20complicated%2C%20I've%20recently%20thought%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20much%20art%20weighs%2C%20because%20a%20wall%20may%20need%20to%20be%20reinforced%20if%20a%20piece%20is%20too%20heavy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20our%20team%20is%20finally%20ready%20to%20install%20a%20piece%2C%20I%20have%20to%20work%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20different%20people%3A%20house%20managers%2C%20conservators%2C%20furniture%20movers%2C%20fine%20art%20shippers.%20I%20really%20enjoy%20getting%20glimpses%20into%20clients'%20homes%2C%20and%20I%20can't%20even%20begin%20to%20describe%20some%20of%20their%20art%20collections.%20But%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20in%20these%20spaces%2C%20and%20a%20few%20rules%20I%20always%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20have%20my%20iPad%20or%20another%20small%20item%2C%20I%20don't%20put%20it%20down%2C%20because%20I%20never%20know%20whether%20something%20is%20a%20chair%20or%20a%20piece%20of%20art.%20I%20also%20make%20sure%20that%20nothing%20is%20hanging%20off%20my%20body%2C%20and%20I%20tell%20art%20handlers%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20remove%20things%20like%20tape%20measures%20from%20their%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20take%20off%20my%20shoes%20or%20use%20shoe%20covers.%20Sometimes%20the%20client%20isn't%20home%2C%20which%20can%20make%20the%20process%20a%20bit%20easier%2C%20but%20I%20always%20try%20to%20be%20in%20and%20out.%20I%20have%20to%20hire%20furniture%20movers%20for%20certain%20projects%2C%20like%20when%20we%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20huge%2C%20beautiful%20stone%20table%20that%20was%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I've%20observed%20that%20a%20room%20is%20really%20warm%20and%20advised%20clients%20to%20check%20the%20temperature%2C%20because%20heat%20can%20damage%20certain%20art.%20Or%20maybe%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20light%20coming%20in%2C%20and%20it's%20worth%20investing%20in%20window%20shades.%20I've%20also%20helped%20clients%20upgrade%20their%20bulbs%20to%20more%20energy-efficient%20ones%20that%20give%20off%20less%20heat%2C%20which%20helps%20preserve%20art%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20clients%20have%20high%20expectations%20of%20us%2C%20as%20they%20should.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburnout-investment-banking-professional-tennis-learned-how-to-quit-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebanker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20it's%20very%20stressful%20in%20a%20different%20way.%20But%20for%20us%2C%20being%20in%20our%20clients'%20homes%20and%20offices%20%E2%80%94%20even%20with%20all%20the%20precautions%20%E2%80%94%20helps%20us%20build%20strong%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-advisor-citi-bank-private-wealth-clients-homes-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766748421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691b559a89026fbb4d0dc6d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fart-advisor-citi-bank-private-wealth-clients-homes-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Carla%20Caputo%2C%20an%20art%20collections%20manager%20for%20Citi's%20high-net-worth%20clients%2C%20reveals%20how%20she%20manages%20logistics%20and%20conducts%20herself%20in%20expensive%20homes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus