s%26quot%3B%20of%20free%20users%2C%20said%20its%20cofounder%2C%20Benoit%20Baylin%2C%20and%20close%20to%20100%2C000%20paying%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20smaller%20apps%20that%20have%20grown%20their%20audiences.%20There's%20Wingman%20(4%2C700%20paying%20customers)%2C%20FireTexts%20(10%2C000%20installs%20a%20month)%2C%20and%20Amori%2C%20one%20of%20the%20few%20VC-backed%20startups%20in%20the%20space%20(10%2C000%20registered%20users).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20startups%20are%20mostly%20oriented%20around%20dating%20apps%20and%20DM%20slides%2C%20though%20they%20can%20also%20be%20used%20for%20flirty%20messages%20far%20beyond%20a%20first%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWho's%20using%20these%20apps%3F%20It's%20hard%20to%20say%2C%20though%20FireTexts%20founder%20Alex%20Vilenchik%20has%20noticed%20a%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20a%20single%20female%20user%20besides%20my%20girlfriend%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22528ad56f-6ddf-4cfd-a63e-8101ce72f098%5C%22%3EThe%20dating%20apps%20make%20their%20move%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20helpers%20grow%2C%20the%20big%20dating%20apps%20are%20threatening%20to%20make%20them%20obsolete%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDating%20apps%20are%20increasingly%20incorporating%20AI%20advisors.%20Tinder%20has%20an%20AI%20photo%20selector%3B%20Hinge%20offers%20advice%20on%20opening%20lines.%20Grindr%20is%20piloting%20its%20own%20Wingman%20product%2C%20and%20Chief%20Product%20Officer%20AJ%20Balance%20said%20that%20feedback%20has%20been%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hinge's%20AI-powered%20conversation%20starter%20feature%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693ae563832e0ef1ead60c37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHinge%20includes%20AI-generated%20advice%20on%20drafting%20an%20opening%20line.%3Cp%3EHinge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20is%20ripe%20for%20an%20acquisition%2C%20though%20none%20of%20the%20founders%20seems%20to%20be%20biting.%20Rizz's%20Khaves%20said%20that%20Match%20Group's%20CTO%20approached%20him%20in%202023%2C%20but%20talks%20ended%20when%20Khaves%20wasn't%20interested%20in%20an%20acquihire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYourMove's%20Mirakyan%20said%20that%20he's%20had%20talks%20with%20multiple%20major%20dating%20app%20companies.%20Roast's%20Baylin%20said%20he%20talked%20to%20Bumble%20and%20Match%20Group%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20unimpressed%20with%20the%20latter's%20current%20efforts.%20Match%20Group%20declined%20to%20confirm%20any%20past%20potential%20acquisition%20conversations%3B%20Bumble%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20see%20the%20Tinder%20photo%20selection%2C%20it's%20really%20far%20behind%20in%20terms%20of%20tech%2C%26quot%3B%20Baylin%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20take%2020%20selfies%20of%20yourself%2C%20those%2020%20are%20going%20to%20pop%20up%20as%20the%20potential%20photo%20options.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(I%20tested%20the%20photo%20selector%20for%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20while%20it%20didn't%20pick%20only%20selfies%2C%20it%20did%20pick%20entirely%20solo%20shots%2C%20breaking%20the%20classic%20dating%20app%20rule%20that%20you%20want%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eat%20least%20some%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Egroup%20shots%20to%20prove%20you%20have%20friends.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20founders%20seemed%20skeptical%20about%20the%20major%20dating%20apps'%20entrance%20into%20the%20space.%20Wingman%20founder%20Rob%20Mariani%20and%20FireText's%20Vilenchik%20both%20suggested%20that%20the%20companies%20were%20too%20politically%20correct%20to%20be%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20they%20able%20to%20make%20their%20AI%20say%2C%20'Well%2C%20dude%2C%20have%20you%20considered%20losing%20weight%3F'%26quot%3B%20Mariani%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20very%20impolite%20thing%20to%20say.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20they%20have%20it%20in%20them%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20the%20AI%20pioneers%20themselves.%20The%20makers%20of%20foundation%20models%20and%20the%20chatbots%20they%20power%20pose%20another%20threat%20to%20the%20AI%20wingman%20startups.%20ChatGPT%20can%20generate%20suggestions%20for%20dating%20app%20messages%20or%20provide%20feedback%20for%20profiles.%20OpenAI%20will%20soon%20allow%20erotica%20for%20adults%2C%20per%20its%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-announces-chatgpt-getting-into-erotica-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20opening%20up%20even%20more%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20founders%20must%20convince%20daters%20to%20seek%20out%20a%20specialized%20product%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20pay%20a%20subscription%20fee%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20turning%20to%20a%20traditional%20chatbot%20or%20a%20built-in%20AI%20tool%20on%20their%20go-to%20dating%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231379795-d53c-4488-95cb-24e6b29b08c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAm%20I%20being%20chatfished%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20thornier%20question%20remains%3A%20Do%20singles%20want%20to%20bring%20AI%20into%20their%20dating%20lives%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kinsey%20Institute%20at%20Indiana%20University%20conducts%20an%20annual%20survey%20of%205%2C000%20daters%20in%20partnership%20with%20Match%20Group.%20This%20year%2C%2026%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20that%20they%20were%20using%20AI%20while%20dating.%20That%20figure%20jumped%20to%2038%25%20for%20active%20daters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKinsey%20Institute%20research%20scientist%20Amanda%20Gesselman%20said%20she%20heard%20anecdotally%20that%20some%20daters%20felt%20like%20they%20were%20chatting%20with%20bots.%2033%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20that%20using%20AI%20to%20generate%20an%20entire%20conversation%20was%20a%20dealbreaker.%20The%20daters%20were%20more%20receptive%20to%20an%20AI-generated%20opening%20line%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20sore%20spot%20was%20AI-altered%20photos%2C%20with%2040%25%20calling%20it%20a%20dealbreaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20some%20hesitancy%20from%20the%20dating%20apps%2C%20too.%20While%20Tinder%20invests%20in%20its%20AI%20photo%20selector%2C%20it's%20still%20holding%20back%20from%20fully%20artificial%20conversations.%20Claire%20Watanabe%2C%20Tinder's%20senior%20director%20of%20product%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Tinder%20should%20%26quot%3Bnever%20feel%20like%20a%20sea%20of%20chatbot-generated%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternally%2C%20we've%20even%20joked%20about%20removing%20the%20paste%20function%20or%20adding%20an%20em%20dash%20detector%20to%20flag%20suspiciously%20'AI-ish'%20writing%2C%26quot%3B%20Watanabe%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20half-serious%2C%20but%20the%20intent%20is%20real.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223065%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daksha%20Franklin%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694ad16a04eda4732f2e0b91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223445%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E36-year-old%20Daksha%20Franklin%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20describe%20her%20dream%20man.%3Cp%3ELAURA_HUERTAS%2FLaura%20Huertas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20efforts%2C%20it's%20still%20unclear%20whether%20AI%20wingmen%20are%20a%20fad%20or%20the%20future.%20Daksha%20Franklin%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20clinical%20hypnotherapist%20from%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20spruce%20up%20her%20dating%20profile%20%E2%80%94%20and%20wasn't%20thrilled%20with%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20didn't%20like%20it%2C%20so%20I%20went%20with%20my%20own%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranklin%20isn't%20an%20AI%20pessimist%2C%20though.%20She%20also%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20describe%20her%20dream%20man%20so%20she%20could%20narrow%20down%20her%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chatbot%20nailed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-wingman-dating-helper-tinder-hinge-pickup-lines-chatgpt-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766741401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693afe3a04eda4732f2d5db6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-wingman-dating-helper-tinder-hinge-pickup-lines-chatgpt-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Daters%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20slide%20into%20the%20DMs%20and%20craft%20Hinge%20profiles.%20A%20crop%20of%20startups%20and%20dating%20apps%20are%20fighting%20for%20these%20AI-powered%20daters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-wingman-dating-helper-tinder-hinge-pickup-lines-chatgpt-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Could%20global%20warming%20paradoxically%20freeze%20the%20planet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766741400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-126187133%2Cimgsize-117532.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Fcould-global-warming-paradoxically-freeze-the-planet-how-tiny-ocean-organisms-could-flip-earths-climate%2Farticleshow%2F126187127.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ancient%20oceans%2C%20driven%20by%20microscopic%20life%2C%20once%20pulled%20vast%20amounts%20of%20carbon%20from%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20leading%20to%20dramatic%20cooling%20and%20ice%20ages.%20This%20biological%20pump%2C%20fueled%20by%20plankton%2C%20highlights%20how%20marine%20ecosystems%20can%20profoundly%20reshape%20global%20climate.%20Today's%20changing%20oceans%20may%20trigger%20similar%2C%20unpredictable%20shift