get%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20it%20multiple%20times%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20job%20will%20be%20affected%2C%20and%20immediately.%20It%20is%20unquestionable.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20lose%20your%20job%20to%20an%20AI%2C%20but%20you're%20going%20to%20lose%20your%20job%20to%20someone%20who%20uses%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20Milken%20Institute's%20Global%20Conference%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20leaders%20echoed%20his%20view%2C%20with%20some%20saying%20that%20younger%20workers%20may%20actually%20have%20an%20edge%20because%20they%20are%20already%20comfortable%20using%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-workforce-future-jobs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20Cleo%20Abram's%20%26quot%3BHuge%20Conversations%26quot%3B%20YouTube%20show%20in%20August%20that%20while%20AI%20will%20inevitably%20wipe%20out%20some%20roles%2C%20college%20graduates%20are%20better%20equipped%20to%20adjust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%2022%20right%20now%20and%20graduating%20college%2C%20I%20would%20feel%20like%20the%20luckiest%20kid%20in%20all%20of%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20bigger%20concern%20is%20how%20older%20workers%20will%20cope%20as%20AI%20reshapes%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgodmother-of-ai-value-of-college-degrees-silicon-valley-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFei-Fei%20Li%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Stanford%20professor%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgodmother%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Tim%20Ferriss%20Show%26quot%3B%20published%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20resistance%20to%20AI%20is%20a%20dealbreaker.%20She%20said%20she%20won't%20hire%20engineers%20who%20refuse%20to%20use%20AI%20tools