https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-career-progression-soft-skills-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoft%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20communication%20and%20collaboration%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20for%20experienced%20workers%20and%20fresh%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20automates%20parts%20of%20our%20job%20and%20makes%20teams%20leaner%2C%20the%20human%20part%20of%20the%20job%20is%20starting%20to%20matter%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247cf38ec-6c23-4126-ab41-c714294f05b4%5C%22%3E3.%20AI%20is%20evolving%20fast%20%E2%80%94%20and%20superintelligence%20is%20coming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20year%20went%20on%2C%20the%20stakes%20around%20AI's%20future%20began%20to%20feel%20bigger%20and%20more%20real.%20Tech%20leaders%20increasingly%20spoke%20about%20chasing%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20or%20AGI%2C%20and%20eventually%20superintelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAGI%20refers%20to%20AI%20systems%20that%20can%20match%20human%20intelligence%20across%20a%20range%20of%20tasks%2C%20while%20superintelligence%20describes%20systems%20that%20surpass%20human%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20said%20in%20September%20that%20society%20needs%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20superintelligence%2C%20which%20could%20arrive%20by%202030.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20established%20Meta's%20Superintelligence%20Labs%20in%20June%20and%20said%20that%20the%20company%20is%20pushing%20toward%20superintelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20leaders%20don't%20want%20to%20miss%20the%20AI%20moment.%20Zuckerberg%20underscored%20that%20urgency%20in%20September%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20rather%20risk%20%26quot%3Bmisspending%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20billion%20dollars%26quot%3B%20than%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-risk-billions-miss-superintelligence-ai-bubble-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elate%20to%20superintelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20tech%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%2