0to%20rebuild%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20by%20reintroducing%20native%20tree%20species%20to%20depleted%20landscapes.%20He%20recalls%20the%20early%20days%20vividly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20visited%20these%20villages%2C%20the%20soil%20was%20exhausted%20and%20the%20air%20heavy%20with%20pollution.%20We%20knew%20planting%20trees%20was%20essential%2C%20but%20the%20real%20challenge%20was%20to%20plant%20hope%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20among%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20seed%20of%20hope%20was%20first%20sown%20in%20March%202019%2C%20when%20the%20foundation%20planted%20saplings%20on%20government%20land%20in%20Badaushi%20Kalan%20village.%20It%20was%20a%20modest%20start%2C%20but%20rooted%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20reviving%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20biodiversity%20with%20native%20species%20like%20desi%20beri%2C%20dhaak%2C%20phulai%2C%20and%20farah.%20These%20hardy%20trees%2C%20once%20central%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20natural%20identity%2C%20restore%20soil%20and%20water%20systems%2C%20support%20wildlife%20habitats%2C%20and%20withstand%20climate%20extremes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roundglass%20Foundation%20encourages%20and%20educates%20the%20youth%20to%20plant%20native%20trees%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20so%20that%20the%20initiative%20continues%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-